  <brief_title>N-3 Fatty Acids for the Prevention of Atrial Fibrillation in Patients With Acute Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>N-3 Fatty Acids for the Prevention of Atrial Fibrillation in Patients With Acute Heart Failure</official_title>
  <sponsors>
